336
00:27:30,260 --> 00:27:32,750
Seven dollars in any rock-and-gem shop.

337
00:27:33,270 --> 00:27:35,730
My normal markup's 20 percent.

338
00:27:35,930 --> 00:27:38,300
But this is a specialty item.

339
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:42,960
