341
00:27:46,250 --> 00:27:48,270
Waste of money, if you ask me.

342
00:27:48,550 --> 00:27:49,840
Why's that?

343
00:27:51,250 --> 00:27:54,280
Folks around this joint
love surprise inspections.

344
00:27:55,890 --> 00:27:57,860
They find it, you're going to lose it.

345
00:27:58,060 --> 00:28:00,150
If they catch you, you don't know me.

346
00:28:00,360 --> 00:28:02,590
Mention my name, we never
do business again.

347
00:28:03,100 --> 00:28:06,190
Not for shoelaces or a stick of gum.
Now you got that?

348
00:28:07,030 --> 00:28:08,590
I understand.

349
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:11,890
Thank you, Mr...

350
00:28:12,100 --> 00:28:13,130
Red.

351
00:28:13,870 --> 00:28:15,170
Name's Red.

352
00:28:16,610 --> 00:28:18,240
Why do they call you that?

353
00:28:22,010 --> 00:28:24,010
Maybe it's because I'm Irish.

354
00:28:32,190 --> 00:28:35,060
I could see why some of the boys
