362
00:29:02,150 --> 00:29:05,950
Let's go! Some of us
got a schedule to keep.

363
00:29:09,290 --> 00:29:11,790
Move it! Come on, move it!

364
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:17,330
How you doing?
How's the wife treating you?

365
00:29:55,470 --> 00:29:56,940
Andy was right.

366
00:29:57,180 --> 00:29:59,410
I finally got the joke.

367
00:29:59,710 --> 00:30:02,110
