volunteered for the job.

407
00:33:42,900 --> 00:33:45,890
Wallace E. Unger.

408
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:48,770
Ellis Redding.

409
00:33:48,970 --> 00:33:50,530
Wouldn't you know it?

410
00:33:50,980 --> 00:33:54,280
Me and some fellows I know
were among the names called.

411
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:56,470
Andrew Dufresne.

412
00:33:56,880 --> 00:33:59,820
